        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/power-berserker/">&lt;p&gt;Simple, priority based, and ranged Power DPS build.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;notes&quot;&gt;Notes&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Power Berserker is a very strong build for instanced content, even with a simplified rotation.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the usage of Spear as the main weapon, it further has high range, allowing you to deal great damage with flexible positioning.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&#x27;s also a great pick for solo gameplay, as it provides itself with good amounts of the most essential offensive boons: Quickness, Fury, and Might.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
